// Scorer service contract.
//
// The scorer-pool is a Python gRPC server on the NAS that fans out to the
// four sub-scorers (BM25 / vector / citation / recency), fuses with
// Reciprocal Rank Fusion (k=60), and reranks the top 50 with an XGBoost
// LambdaMART head. Results stream back to the gateway in three waves
// (first 5 @ 200ms, next 10 @ 500ms, final 35 @ 1000ms).
//
// Spec source of truth: docs/EVIDENCELENS_SPEC.md sections 5.5 and 6.

